# 16.14 Common Errors

### Deprecated Gemini Model

```
404

Model not found
```

Solution

```
gemini-2.5-flash
```

---

### Worker Timeout

```
WORKER TIMEOUT
```

Possible causes

- MCP session failure
- Runtime dependency
- Long-running tool

---

### Failed MCP Session

```
Failed to create MCP session
```

Possible causes

- Missing runtime
- Invalid API key
- MCP server unavailable

---

### Google Maps Authentication

Symptoms

```
ADC

Authentication
```

Verify

```
GOOGLE_MAPS_API_KEY
```

---

### Filesystem MCP Failure

Symptoms

```
Timeout

Session Failure
```

Verify

```
Node

npm

npx
```

